        "feedback": "The text effectively establishes the relevance of the topic by connecting drone swarm technology to current geopolitical events (Russia-Ukraine war) and the rapid advancement of AI. It successfully highlights the potential for automation in rescue missions, which aligns with the thesis title. The inclusion of local statistics (Latvia) strengthens the argument for local relevance.",
